definition.text: This book will walk you through everything you need to know about the Docs.

paragraphs.text: Superalgos->I->Docs Basics->Read Chapter I to learn the basics concepts. They are the foundation that will let you understand the commands and styles explained later in this book.

Superalgos->II->Docs Commands->The Docs include a powerful command line interface that allows you to quickly fire commands from the search box. Dive into Chapter II to learn the details of each available command.
